   @{fg shine}@{b}Annotate 3.0.1  by  Doug Bakewell & Daniel Westerberg@{ub}
   ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{fg text}

    A comprehensive text editor with programmer's features like syntax highlighting
    and macros written for AmigaOS 2.0 and up, ported to AmigaOS 4.0, backported to
    AmigaOS 3 and sideported to MorphOS and AROS.

    @{fg fill}Compile date: 2012-12-01@{fg text}



